      <p>Every ingredient, every percentage, every source — listed plainly. No proprietary blends hiding what's actually inside.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon">✦</div>
      <h4>Proof Over Promises</h4>
      <p>We publish our trial results, good and middling. If a formula doesn't outperform what's already on the market, it doesn't ship.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-icon">✦</div>
      <h4>Slow by Design</h4>
      <p>Small batches, considered packaging, no seasonal drops for the sake of drops. We'd rather make six things well than sixty adequately.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

